        "content": "<p>Hey! I currently have a lean game server setup as a side project. However I can't seem to be able to enter calc mode within the client.</p>\n<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/4MnUslwwym9LdBbIVTuW_CmC/Screenshot-2024-11-16-150624.png\">Screenshot 2024-11-16 150624.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/4MnUslwwym9LdBbIVTuW_CmC/Screenshot-2024-11-16-150624.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2024-11-16 150624.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"1266x634\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/3121/4MnUslwwym9LdBbIVTuW_CmC/Screenshot-2024-11-16-150624.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div><p>Since it is not a tactic and part of lean itself, is there any way to enable it for the game?</p>\n<p>It works fine in visual studios though:<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/brmRz7vQioADxlQ2j1FlvydE/t2.png\">t2.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/brmRz7vQioADxlQ2j1FlvydE/t2.png\" title=\"t2.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"1810x759\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/3121/brmRz7vQioADxlQ2j1FlvydE/t2.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div><p>Thanks for the help!</p>",
