        "content": "<p>Lines like <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/NNG4/blob/66b27f382aa68b1651cc41a855447079a952d678/Game/Levels/Tutorial/L02rw.lean#L155\">this</a> are what enables tactics to be used in \"regular\" mode. Also look above that line for how I set up the docstring for the tactic.</p>",
